column5: I would like to introduce everyone to our new fishing partner and son Janzen Tyler Joe . He came in at 6.9 lbs on friday at 12;34 pm .My wife is one hell of trooper   and we hope to get him out fishing in a couple of years !
A very ginormous congratulations to you sir!
Congrats man I know the feeling my son is just a little over 2 and he can side cast its hillarious
congrats, but no need to wait for a couple years
Fantastic news and congratulations to your entire family !!
Congratulations to you and your family
Congrats! When I read the title I thought it was either a baby or a puppy..All the better this way!
Congratulations! I'm sure you will get him out fishing as soon as it is feasible.
Thanks everyone for the best wish's...mom ,Janzen and dad are doing well for first time parents !
